{"tid":2078617,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"110萬賑災 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-06-25T07:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T07:37:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c39991711573ff78ad417f07eb39d4b0bf354f40","tid":2078617,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200625/20943530/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200625%2F20943530%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=ffe00ce4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200625%2F20943530%2F&h=71ef381e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200625/20943530/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n110萬賑災 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200625/large/1592983669_6c2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200625%2Flarge%2F1592983669_6c2e.jpg&h=6f841800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法新社<br />\n<br />\n特區政府批出110萬撥款，向廣西水災災民賑災。<br />\n<br />\n110萬！我還以為看錯了，<br />\n..............................<br />\n，災民連乞丐都不如。<br />\n<br />\n110萬這種數目，誰會放在眼裏？連窮鄉僻壤的鄉村村委書記都嫌棄出手太低吧？用110萬去賑災，除了譏諷強國水利工程及排水系統是豆腐渣之外，還譏諷強國政府連110萬元都掏不出來。<br />\n<br />\n最大的問題是，發生水災的明明是重慶，廣西甚麼時候成了災區？選擇向廣西賑災的理據是甚麼？為甚麼厚廣西薄四川？事實上，一年一度的「廣西荔枝狗肉節」今年如期在夏至這天展開，為期十天，並未因武漢肺炎而取消。這幾天應該舉行得如火如荼，廣西人正大啖大啖進食荔枝和狗肉，歡樂無比。他們甚麼時候成了災民了？<br />\n<br />\n從網絡視頻可見，<br />\n......................................<br />\n：「狗肉要柴火大灶燜煮才夠入味好吃！」<br />\n<br />\n人家大碗喝酒、<br />\n.................................<br />\n？太侮辱了吧？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"bd66460233b5f2ab90003456a4e88ac9030b8990","tid":2078617,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"［行動po置頂］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}